name: Forbidden Light Booster Box
extCardText:
Each booster box contains 36 packs. Each pack contains 10 cards.
Taking the Pokemon world by surprise, Necrozma has absorbed a Legendary Pokemon and taken on a new form as Ultra Necrozma-GX! Other Pokemon gather to welcome this new light...or to resist it. Lucario-GX, Greninja-GX, Zygarde-GX, Yveltal-GX, Naganadel-GX, even Volcanion and the majestic Arceus must choose a side. Discover awesome Pokemon and mysterious treasures in the Pokemon TCG: Sun & Moon - Forbidden Light expansion!

Details:
• Over 130 cards
• 5 Prism Star cards featuring a new game mechanic
• 8 Pokemon-GX and 6 Ultra Beasts
• 15 Trainer cards and 2 Special Energy cards

name: Forbidden Light Elite Trainer Box
extCardText:
Necrozma’s Power Knows No Limits!

Taking the Pokemon world by surprise, Necrozma has absorbed a Legendary Pokemon and taken on a new form as Ultra Necrozma-GX! Other Pokemon gather to welcome this new light...or to resist it. Lucario-GX, Greninja-GX, Zygarde-GX, Yveltal-GX, Naganadel-GX, even Volcanion and the majestic Arceus must choose a side. Discover awesome Pokemon.

Elite Trainer Box includes:
• 8 Pokemon TCG: Sun & Moon - Forbidden Light booster packs
• 65 card sleeves featuring Ultra Necrozma!
• 45 Pokemon TCG Energy cards
• A player’s guide to the Sun & Moon - Forbidden Light expansion
• 6 damage-counter dice
• 1 competition-legal coin-flip die
• 2 acrylic condition markers and 1 acrylic GX marker
• A collector’s box to hold everything, with 4 dividers to keep it organized
• A code card for the Pokemon Trading Card Game Online

name: Forbidden Light 3-Card Booster Pack
extCardText:
Each pack contains 3 cards.
Taking the Pokemon world by surprise, Necrozma has absorbed a Legendary Pokemon and taken on a new form as Ultra Necrozma-GX! Other Pokemon gather to welcome this new light...or to resist it. Lucario-GX, Greninja-GX, Zygarde-GX, Yveltal-GX, Naganadel-GX, even Volcanion and the majestic Arceus must choose a side. Discover awesome Pokemon and mysterious treasures in the Pokemon TCG: Sun & Moon - Forbidden Light expansion!

Set Details:
• Over 130 cards
• 5 Prism Star cards featuring a new game mechanic
• 8 Pokemon-GX and 6 Ultra Beasts
• 15 Trainer cards and 2 Special Energy cards
